{"tid":2361813,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美帝足球年輕勢力","createTime":"2021-01-11T04:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T14:50:28.000Z","uid":106189,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1028d4ecd6f0501bcf6954c4be932bdcac7c0678","tid":2361813,"uid":106189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"有留意近年美帝足球，有好多年輕球員彈起，<br />\n仲有好多球員都去左國搵食<br />\n未有咁多新血球員彈起<br />\n美帝足球主要靠招有美帝血統入黎<br />\n奇哥嗰段期間最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奇哥落台<br />\n迎來新血球員彈起<br />\n美帝咁多新血主要原因<br />\n唔靠大學足球輸入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇美帝體育都知有個system<br />\nNCAA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但NCAA都唔流行足球<br />\nMLS SuperDraft係有<br />\n但有幾多個彈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以08年美帝先set Homegrown Player Rule<br />\n美職建立自己青訓梯隊<br />\n美職可以簽自己青訓上一線隊<br />\n所以先會有tyler adams McKennie 小Reyna出現<br />\n因為佢地都無踢大學波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9376bbb672f136f702a735431d74e269aa42d072","tid":2361813,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"樓主覺得ncaa水平如何"},{"pid":"2a841c123f5119053090844eb715ba617b71fafe","tid":2361813,"uid":255704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9376bbb672f136f702a735431d74e269aa42d072","tid":2361813,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"樓主覺得ncaa水平如何"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:37:47.000Z","msg":"差 同歐洲球會青訓冇得比<br />\n不過美國人身體質素高<br />\n同埋重視體育訓練<br />\n有天份嘅球員<br />\n可以進一步去歐洲訓練<br />\n大部份出名嘅美國球員<br />\n都係來自足球世家<br />\n名宿之後"},{"pid":"efad6d76918db7e958687d556085e64ff55e36c6","tid":2361813,"uid":255704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a841c123f5119053090844eb715ba617b71fafe","tid":2361813,"uid":255704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9376bbb672f136f70